PrecisOrder confirming a request made to Mr. BILL ATTEWELL, M.P., to travel to Yerevan, Armenia, from September 18th to the 23rd, 1991, in order to observe the unfolding of the referendum on the question of independence on behalf of the Secretary of State for External Affairs.
